snippet.title: Sonic Megamix Mania | SHC2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
After 3 years of steady development, we are finally back at The Sonic Hacking Contest this year!
Get the mod here once the contest week starts: https://shc.zone/entries/contest2023/906

We assure you that the wait's been worth it as this contest we are arriving with a whole 20 acts, spread across two modes, a whole OST release, and much more!

Editing by: Balibali @Balibali418 
Trailer Music by: Daan Demmers @DaanDemmers. 

Check out our Discord and Twitter for more information and insights!
Discord: https://discord.gg/dBUqJ5f
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MegamixMania
